'''1999年伊茲密特地震'''又稱作'''科賈埃利地震'''或'''格爾居克地震'''，是一場發生於1999年8月17日清晨3點1分40秒的地震，震央在土耳其西北部[[科賈埃利省|科賈埃利省]]的首府[[伊茲密特|伊茲密特]]。本地震的[[矩震級|矩震級]]達到7.6，[[麥加利地震震度|麥加利地震震度]]為9（IX）。37秒的搖晃造成超過17,000人死亡與50萬人無家可歸<ref name="marza"/>。伊茲密特和鄰近城鎮均遭受嚴重的破壞。

== 概述 ==

[[File:USGS_Shakemap_-_1999_Izmit_earthquake.jpg|thumb]]
本次地震肇因於[[北安那托利亞斷層|北安那托利亞斷層]]西側的錯動。構成土耳其大部分領土的[[安那托利亞板塊|安那托利亞板塊]]每年受到北方[[歐亞大陸板塊|歐亞大陸板塊]]及東南部的[[阿拉伯板塊|阿拉伯板塊]]擠壓而向西移動約2.5公分<ref name="USGS_TS">{{cite web|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eqarchives/year/1999/1999_08_17_ts.php|title=Tectonic summary|last=USGS|date=June 18, 2012|work=Historic Earthquakes Magnitude 7.6 TURKEY 1999 August 17 00:01:39 UTC|accessdate=2 February 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929015334/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eqarchives/year/1999/1999_08_17_ts.php|archive-date=2015-09-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。絕大部分土耳其地震都發生在北安那托利亞斷層和[[東安那托利亞斷層|東安那托利亞斷層]]。

斷層沿著[[伊茲密特灣|伊茲密特灣]]破裂，產生了從[[迪茲傑|迪茲傑]]至[[馬摩拉海|馬摩拉海]]{{convert|150|km|mi|sp=us}}的破裂帶，及5.7公尺的地表偏移量<ref name="Reilinger">{{cite journal|last=Reilinger|first=R.E.|author2=Ergintav S., Bürgmann R., McClusky S., Lenk O., Barka A., Gurkan O., Hearn L., Feigl K.L., Cakmak R., Aktug B., Ozener H. & Töksoz M.N.|year=2000|title=Coseismic and Postseismic Fault Slip for the 17 August 1999, M = 7.5, Izmit, Turkey Earthquake|journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]]|publisher=[[American_Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Science|American Association for the Advancement of Science]]|volume=289|pages=1519–1524|url=ftp://www.ncedc.org/outgoing/burgmann/REPRINTS/Reilinger_SCIENCE2000.pdf|doi=10.1126/science.289.5484.1519}}</ref>。

== 災情 ==
震央離[[伊斯坦堡|伊斯坦堡]]僅{{convert|70|km|mi}}，給伊斯坦堡的[[土耳其人口|人口稠密區]]帶來衝擊，工業方面亦造成包括數間發電廠、煉油廠及[[土耳其海軍|海軍]]基地的損失<ref name="Barka">{{citation|title=The 17 August 1999 Izmit Earthquake|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/content/285/5435/1858|first=A.|last=Barka|year=1999|journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]]|publisher=[[American_Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Science|American Association for the Advancement of Science]]|volume=285|number=5435|pages=1858–1859|doi=10.1126/science.285.5435.1858|accessdate=2015-11-01|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145525/http://www.sciencemag.org/content/285/5435/1858|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根據當局於1999年10月9日發布的數據，共17,127人死亡及43,959人負傷，同時有部分非官方資料顯示死亡人數將近45,000人<ref name="marza">{{Cite journal | last = Marza | first = Vasile I. | title = On the death toll of the 1999 Izmit (Turkey) major earthquake | year = 2004 | place = ESC General Assembly Papers, Potsdam | publisher = European Seismological Commission | url = http://www.esc-web.org/papers/potsdam_2004/ss_1_marza.pdf | accessdate = 5 March 2008 <!--DASHBot--> | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080409044047/http://www.esc-web.org/papers/potsdam_2004/ss_1_marza.pdf | archivedate = 2008-04-09 | deadurl = yes | journal =  | author =  }}</ref>。

此外，[[歐洲E80公路|歐洲E80公路]]的20座橋梁及5條隧道無法行駛<ref>Lusas software, [http://www.lusas.com/case/bridge/mustafa.html "Seismic Assessment of the Mustafa Inan Viaduct"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lusas.com/case/bridge/mustafa.html |date=20201205162533 }}</ref>。土耳其唯一的國有煉油廠[[Tüpraş|Tüpraş]]的[[石腦油|石腦油]]槽發生火警，5天後才得以撲滅<ref name=Scawthorn>{{cite book|title=Fire Following Earthquake|year=2005|publisher=ASCE, NFPA|location=Reston, VA|isbn=9780784407394|url=http://www.asce.org/Product.aspx?id=2147485909&productid=5362|editor=Scawthorn, Eidinger, Schiff|access-date=2015-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928111244/http://www.asce.org/Product.aspx?id=2147485909&productid=5362|archive-date=2013-09-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
