=== 海嘯 ===
[[馬摩拉海|馬摩拉海]]因地震引發2.5公尺高的海嘯，造成155人喪生<ref name="NGDC_T">{{cite web|url=http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/results?eq_0=5527&t=101650&s=18&d=99,91,95,93&nd=display|title=Tsunami event|last=[[National_Geophysical_Data_Center|National Geophysical Data Center]]|accessdate=2 February 2013|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107232033/https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/results?eq_0=5527&t=101650&s=18&d=99,91,95,93&nd=display|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 救援行動 ==
[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]、[[以色列|以色列]]、[[法國|法國]]、[[南韓|南韓]]、[[比利時|比利時]]、[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]、[[德國|德國]]、[[波蘭|波蘭]]、[[希臘|希臘]]、[[奧地利|奧地利]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]、[[美國|美國]]、[[冰島|冰島]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]、[[埃及|埃及]]、[[英國|英國]]、[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]、[[義大利|義大利]]與[[亞塞拜然|亞塞拜然]]、[[中華民國|中華民國]]等國的救援團隊<ref>{{cite book|editor-last=Tang|editor-first=Alex K.|title=Izmit (Kocaeli), Turkey, earthquake of August 17, 1999 including Duzce Earthquake of November 12, 1999 Lifeline Performance|publisher=[[American_Society_of_Civil_Engineers|American Society of Civil Engineers]]|year=2000|page=259|url=http://books.google.com/?id=hHfQJ1nDXvkC&pg=PA255&lpg=PA255&dq=1999+izmit+turkey+earthquake+international+response&q=1999%20izmit%20turkey%20earthquake%20international%20response|isbn=978-0-7844-0494-2}}</ref><ref name="psp-nowysacz.pl">{{Cite web |url=http://www.psp-nowysacz.pl/content.php?body=page&name=historia5 |title=Komenda Miejska Państwowej Straży Pożarnej w Nowym Sączu<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-11-01 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902050254/https://www.psp-nowysacz.pl/content.php?body=page&name=historia5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、多家[[非政府組織|非政府組織]]及[[紅新月會|紅新月會]]大都在地震發生兩天內抵達災區展開搜救行動。

時任美國總統[[比爾·柯林頓|比爾·柯林頓]]及時任巴基斯坦總理[[納瓦茲·夏立夫|納瓦茲·夏立夫]]都在地震發生後半年內前往重災區探視災民<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://photos.state.gov/galleries/ankara/9104/between_friends_photo_exhibit/12.html |title=Bill Clinton visits İzmit,Turkey |accessdate=2015-11-01 |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108145636/https://photos.state.gov/galleries/ankara/9104/between_friends_photo_exhibit/12.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

